severity: medium
environment: Project workspace execution context for Linked-test sandbox project/global extension parity (pm CLI + Node/pnpm toolchain).
repro_steps: Install extension-defined custom type then run same list/search command directly and through linked pm test run.
resolution: implemented
expected_result: Linked sandbox and workspace commands share type-filter acceptance for extension-defined types.
actual_result: Linked sandbox rejects custom type filter with core-only allowed list.
affected_version: 2026.3.12
component: linked-test-sandbox
regression: true
customer_impact: Custom-schema teams cannot rely on linked test evidence consistency.
